<nowiki><p><a href="https://digital-scriptorium.org/">Digital Scriptorium</a></nowiki>. Image database of medieval and renaissance manuscripts that unites scattered resources from many (primarily U.S.) institutions into an international tool for teaching and research.<nowiki></p></nowiki>

<nowiki><p>Dublin, University College <a href="http://digital.ucd.ie/view/iberian:1">Iberian Books. Digital Library</a></nowiki>. Catalogue of books printed 1472-1700; links to digitized copies.<nowiki></p></nowiki>

