<nowiki><p><a href="http://atlas.fcsh.unl.pt/cartoweb35/atlas.php?lang=en">Atlas Cartografia Histórica</a></nowiki>. (Portugal) Map based on Parish Descriptions of 1758. Good for searching small villages and places. Universidade Nova de Lisboa, Faculdade de Ciências Sociais e Humanas (FCSH).

<nowiki></p></nowiki><nowiki><p><a href="https://atlas.lib.uiowa.edu/">Atlas of Early Printing</a></nowiki>. University of Iowa Libraries.  Interactive map with timeline.<nowiki></p></nowiki>

